description:
An All-New Marvel Now title. Continued from SUPERIOR SPIDER-MAN (2013). Peter Parker returns as Spider-Man. The series lasted for 18 regular issues, with a few special Point One issues. After issues 18, the series ended due to the Secret Wars event and was replaced with the Amazing Spider-Man: Renew Your Vows tie-in mini-series. After the events of Secret Wars, the series was restarted as The Amazing Spider-Man Vol 4.

The series also had an The Amazing Spider-Man Special one-shot.
